<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Failed - Action Required</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .alert-box { background-color: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; color: #721c24; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; }
    .cta-button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3); }
    .payment-details { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .grace-period { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; color: #856404; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .urgent-badge { background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
    .deadline-countdown { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>‚ö†Ô∏è Payment Failed</h1>
      <p>Action Required to Continue Your Service</p>
      <div class="urgent-badge">
        IMMEDIATE ATTENTION NEEDED
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name || @user.email.split('@').first.titleize %>,</p>

      <p>We were unable to process your subscription payment for your XSpaceGrow <%= @plan.name %> plan. To ensure uninterrupted service for your IoT devices, please update your payment information immediately.</p>

      <!-- Alert Box -->
      <div class="alert-box">
        <h4>üö® Service Interruption Warning</h4>
        <p><strong>Your account will be suspended if payment is not received by <%= @grace_period_end.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.</strong></p>
        <p>This may affect device monitoring, data collection, and alert notifications.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Payment Details -->
      <div class="payment-details">
        <h3>üí≥ Failed Payment Details</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
          <span>Plan:</span>
          <span><strong><%= @plan.name %> Plan</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
          <span>Amount:</span>
          <span><strong>$<%= sprintf("%.2f", @amount) %> <%= @currency.upcase %></strong></span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
          <span>Reason:</span>
          <span><%= @user_friendly_message %></span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0;">
          <span>Invoice ID:</span>
          <span><%= @invoice_id %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Grace Period Countdown -->
      <div class="deadline-countdown">
        <h3>‚è∞ Grace Period</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">
          <strong><%= (((@grace_period_end - Time.current) / 1.day).ceil) %> days remaining</strong>
        </p>
        <p>Service suspension date: <strong><%= @grace_period_end.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Retry Payment CTA -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @retry_url %>" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
          üîÑ Update Payment Method
        </a>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">
          Secure payment processing with SSL encryption
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What Happens Next -->
      <div class="grace-period">
        <h4>üìã What Happens Next?</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Update Payment:</strong> Click the button above to update your payment method</li>
          <li><strong>Automatic Retry:</strong> We'll attempt to process payment again within 24 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Service Continues:</strong> Your devices remain active during the grace period</li>
          <li><strong>Suspension Warning:</strong> Service will be suspended if payment isn't resolved by the deadline</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Common Payment Issues -->
      <div style="background-color: #e8f4f8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h4>üí° Common Payment Issues & Solutions</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Expired Card:</strong> Update with your new card expiration date</li>
          <li><strong>Insufficient Funds:</strong> Ensure adequate balance or use a different payment method</li>
          <li><strong>Bank Decline:</strong> Contact your bank to authorize XSpaceGrow transactions</li>
          <li><strong>Address Mismatch:</strong> Verify billing address matches your bank records</li>
          <li><strong>International Cards:</strong> Ensure your card supports international transactions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service Impact -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Don't Lose Your Data Protection</h3>
        <p>Your XSpaceGrow <%= @plan.name %> plan provides:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>‚úÖ Real-time device monitoring and alerts</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Historical data preservation</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Custom threshold notifications</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Advanced analytics and reporting</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Priority technical support</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Update your payment to maintain these benefits.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Support -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h4>Need Help? ü§ù</h4>
        <p>Our billing support team is ready to assist:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>üìß Email: <a href="mailto:billing@xspacegrow.com">billing@xspacegrow.com</a></li>
          <li>üí¨ Live Chat: Available 24/7 in your dashboard</li>
          <li>üìû Phone: 1-800-XSPACE-1 (urgent billing issues)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        We value your business and want to keep your IoT monitoring running smoothly. Please resolve this payment issue at your earliest convenience.<br><br>
        <strong>The XSpaceGrow Billing Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        XSpaceGrow ‚Ä¢ IoT Device Management Platform<br>
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>">Dashboard</a> ‚Ä¢ 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/account/billing">Update Payment</a> ‚Ä¢ 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/support">Support</a>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
        Subscription ID: <%= @subscription.id %> ‚Ä¢ Invoice #<%= @invoice_id %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>